post.description:
This endpoint allows the creation of multiple tipos de documento at once.
The request body must contain an array of tipos de documento to be added.
Requer autorização via Chave de API.
            
### Request Example:
    POST /api/integrations/document-type
    {
        "tiposDocumento": [
            {
                "descricao": "NF-e"
            }
        ]
    }

Requer autorização via Chave de API.
Accepts a batch of up to 100 finance situation records in a single request.
            
**Request body example:**

    POST /api/integrations/finance-situation
    {
        "financeSituation": [
            {
                "code": 1,
                "description": "Active",
                "fix": false,
                "sell_operation": 0
            }
        ]
    }
